    ''' <summary>
    ''' Commandline call: Update/Sync playcounts of movies and episodes
    ''' </summary>
    ''' <remarks>
    ''' TODO: Needs some testing (error handling..)!? Idea: Can be executed via commandline to update/sync playcounts of movies and episodes
